All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
Character
Abstract character class that contains main fields needed for implementing the player, enemy and npc characters in the game.
Enemy
Enemy class contains information about enemies.
Field  
Game
The Game class contains the random map generation, as well as handles the movement of the player and interaction with the faced objects.
Interactive
Abstract class to make fields interactive.
Inventory
Inventory class contains a list of inventory items as well as its capacity.
Item
Item class contains items that go into the inventory.
Menu
The main class for the project Dream Realm.
NPC
NPC class contains information about NPCs.
Player
Player class contains information about the player.
Position
Abstract class that adds position element to the needed classes.
Trap
Trap class represents the traps you can find in game.
